{"id": "1368965706787455128", "channel_id": "1368965706787455128", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "我知道字面上寫「戰鬥開始時，使所有敵人……」意思是戰鬥開始那一刻在場上的敵人，所以我是想建議改成「給自己觸手最終傷害+15%」的buff取代給敵人debuff。\n\n作為一個限定會被中場小怪gank有點落漆吧？\n\n然後領航的數字顯示實際也慢了，顯示533實際打出來是555，那是吃到領航buff之後的數字，最後觸腕傷害才更新成正確的數值。\n- 領航卡面明明寫8力量8觸傷，結果出來卻是7力？觸傷，總共+11觸傷。\n- 從這裡也可以看出中場小怪沒受到觸腕傷害+15%的debuff，不然應該是6百多傷害。", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T15:00:58.651000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1368965707219599380", "filename": "Screenshot_20250505_230033_YouTube.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174272, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368965706787455128/1368965707219599380/Screenshot_20250505_230033_YouTube.jpg?ex=69cbe1aa&is=69ca902a&hm=ea63bf55c42f28edab50e2ca351791d1785731e184479abc0bc7c1084523e93c&"}, {"id": "1368965707915726908", "filename": "Screenshot_20250505_230019_YouTube.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 221751, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368965706787455128/1368965707915726908/Screenshot_20250505_230019_YouTube.jpg?ex=69cbe1aa&is=69ca902a&hm=4737b0cd38e1e4296cba49077b354f6e0dfcd90bb09b4378779e4f51faef8b27&"}, {"id": "1368965708301598780", "filename": "Screenshot_20250505_225239_YouTube.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 202454, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368965706787455128/1368965708301598780/Screenshot_20250505_225239_YouTube.jpg?ex=69cbe1ab&is=69ca902b&hm=c9c35f8c4ab1b81a2e3daf850b44ff8df4c3a8da245afcbd6f91594c9b54848f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368965706787455128", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "克珀珊特領航Bug與靈塑加強建議", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497"]}
